### =====================================================================
### Inquiry API  (base route: api/inquiry/)  - third-party inquiry services
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### BillInfo
POST {{host}}/api/inquiry/BillInfo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "billId": "1234567890",
  "paymentId": "12345678"
}

### ZipCodeToAddressDetail
POST {{host}}/api/inquiry/ZipCodeToAddressDetail
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "zipCode": "1234567890",
  "refresh": false
}

### VehicleViolationDetail
POST {{host}}/api/inquiry/VehicleViolationDetail
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "nationalCode": "1234567890",
  "phoneNumber": "09120000000",
  "licencePlate": "12A34567",
  "refresh": false
}

